text:
Is there anything strange... about the costume...?
Am I wearing it properly...?

Yeah, it's fine. Besides,
the stylist checked it thoroughly, didn't they?

With this costume...
our fans will see it...

Looking forward to it...
and feeling nervous...!

...Yeah, that's true.
I'm excited too, and a little nervous.

Producer-san, you're also...
matching with Tenka...!
